Restructured script (hopefully the last time...). The basic syntax now is

arxiv_script AX_ID COMMAND.

(note: later want to change arxiv_script to axs.) This two main advantages:
- the user can simply erase the command and change it (e.g. from 'show' to 'get') without having to move beyond AX_ID as before.
- we can now control the existence of AX_ID directly with cli() and do not have to repeat it in each command!

Finally, we use

arxiv_script --set-directory / --set-bib-file

to set the default download directory and bib file using eager options. This is nicer than extra commands as before.
